article.headline: Lipscomb 77, Stetson 53
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. (AP) -- LaKory Daniels scored 22 points to help Lipscomb beat Stetson 77-53 on Saturday. Brandon Brown added 12 points and six rebounds and Eddie Ard contributed 11 points and five rebounds for the Bisons (10-13, 4-5 Atlantic Sun Conference). Lipscomb dominated the entire game, leading 45-34 in the first half and 32-19 in the second. The Bisons led by as much as 26 points in the second half, and the lead never changed in the game. The Bisons also took advantage of turnovers by the Hatters (10-13, 5-4), scoring 17 points to Stetson's 8 points. The Hatters only had one player who scored double-digits, Garfield Blair, who added 10 points and grabbed four rebounds.
